name: MapKeyDiff_diffTest
description: Unit tests for the MapKeyDiff.diff method, which compares two maps and identifies differences in keys.

test_cases.name: testDiff_BothMapsNull
test_cases.description: Tests the diff method when both input maps are null.

test_cases.name: testDiff_LeftMapNull
test_cases.description: Tests the diff method when the left map is null and the right map is not null.

test_cases.name: testDiff_RightMapNull
test_cases.description: Tests the diff method when the right map is null and the left map is not null.

test_cases.name: testDiff_BothMapsNotNull
test_cases.description: Tests the diff method when both input maps are not null and contain different keys.
